## How to Install

### Binary Installation

```sh
ARCH=$(uname -m | sed 's/aarch64/arm64/' | sed 's/x86_64/amd64/')
URL_PREFIX="https://github.com/{{ .Env.USERNAME }}/{{ .ProjectName }}/releases/download/{{ .Tag }}"
BINARY_NAME="{{ .ProjectName }}" ;VERSION="{{ .Version }}"
FILE_NAME="${BINARY_NAME}_${VERSION}_linux_${ARCH}.tar.gz"
wget "${URL_PREFIX}/${FILE_NAME}" && tar -zxvf "${FILE_NAME}" "${BINARY_NAME}" && chmod +x "${BINARY_NAME}" && mv "${BINARY_NAME}" /usr/bin
```

