### Yum Repository Installation

Add the following content to ``/etc/yum.repos.d/sealos.repo`:

```
[sealos]
name=Sealos Repository
baseurl=https://yum.repo.sealos.io/
enabled=1
gpgcheck=0
```

Then run:

```shell
yum install sealos
```

### APT Repository Installation

Add the following content to `/etc/apt/sources.list.d/sealos.list`:


```
deb [trusted=yes] https://apt.repo.sealos.io/ /
```

Then run:

```shell
apt-get update
apt-get install sealos
```
